		{"id":"a57e8afba032e2c7","x":1440,"y":20,"width":800,"height":460,"type":"text","text":"# Snaggle Tooth\n## Level 2 Solo monster\nHP: ***75***\nArmor: ***Medium***\nSaves: +STR -INT\n### Actions\n- **Move & Hack***: Move 8, attack for 1d8+2; on Damage **Prone**\n- **Batter Up**: 1d8+2, on damage: they are hit towards another hero within 6 spaces. Both make a DC 12 DEX save or take 1d8+2 damage and re knocked Prone, half damage on save.\n### Bloodied\n@37 HP Snaggel Tooth's Damage increases to 1d12+2\n### Last Stand\nSnaggel Tooth is dying! 20 more damage and he dies. Until then Snaggle Tooth can move **6** spaces and use **Batter UP** each turn."}
